Author: Lauda
Title: [BOUNTY][FIN] 🔥 Vena.network - Open Protocol for Tokenzined Asset Financing 🔥
Body: Vena.network Bounty Campaign  |  ANN Thread -  TBA  |  Website  |  Twitter  |  Facebook  | Telegram  |  Github  |   Vena.network Bounty will have a duration of around ~12 weeks has ended. Total tokens available for bounty: 10 000 000 (1% of the total supply).   Bounty Allocation Twitter & Weibo Campaign: 12%. Facebook & Wechat Campaign: 12%. Blog and Article Campaign: 8%. Video Campaign: 5%. Telegram Campaign: 22%. Lucky Draw: 6%. Translation Campaign: Cancelled. Signature Campaign: 5%. Reserved: 25%.   General terms Rewards are given out in the form of stakes. Each stake will represent a % of the total pool. We reserve the right not to accept any members without having to explicitly explain why. We reserve the right to change bounty campaign rules anytime during the campaign. If you have any questions regarding the bounty campaign, please post them only in this thread. Each week will end every Monday between 7-9 AM UTC. Not submitting a week's report will mean that you won't receive stakes for that week. The reserve is allocated for future contributions to the Vena projects by the Vena team. Users can join the campaign with the Copper Membership. Weibo & WeChat campaigns will be handled by the Vena team. For any issues or questions about the campaign join the project Telegram group: https://t.me/vena_network, and ask the bounty manager: @GrumpyKitty.  Payment terms There will be a three-month lockup period (date from listing in exchange) of all bounty tokens and tokens will be distributed evenly by 1/3 for every month since the completion of lockup period. Some campaigns may have additional small requirements for withdrawal (e.g. send out an invite).   Authentication Format: Proof of authentication is only required once for all campaigns that you join! Code: ##PROOF OF AUTHENTICATION## Bitcointalk Profile Link: Campaigns: ETH Address:  The weekly report format is only required for Twitter and Facebook campaigns! Report Format: Code: Week #: Bitcointalk Profile Link: Campaign: Spreadsheet #: ETH Address :   Vena Twitter & Weibo Campaign Twitter Rules Must follow this page. Must have at least 500 followers. Every Twitter account must have at least 90% real followers. Your Twitter account will be checked with twitteraudit.com. The account must be registered before March 2018. The account must not have more than 15k tweets. Must retweet at least 5 tweets weekly (or retweet 3 tweets and make 2 custom tweets). Weibo Rules Must follow Vena official account in Weibo . Every Weibo account / Weibo account must have at least 90% real followers. Your Weibo account will be checked. The account must be registered before March 2018. Must repost at least 5 posts weekly (or repost 3 weibo and make 2 custom weibo).  Rewards 1 stake weekly.  How to Apply for Twitter Week 12 - Closed.  How to Apply for Weibo Use the Weibo Application Form.  Spreadsheet (Twitter)  Vena Facebook & Wechat Campaign Facebook Rules Must follow this page. Must have at least 500 real friends. You must like and then share at least 5 posts per week. Wechat Rules Must follow Wechat official account “Vena洛书协议” of Vena. Must have at least 500 real friends. ou must share at least 2 posts of Vena Network to Wechat group or your Wechat Moments per week.  Rewards 1 stake weekly.  How to Apply for Facebook Week 12 - Closed.   How to Apply for WeChat Use the WeChat application form.  Spreadsheet (Facebook)   Vena Blog and Article Campaign Rules The piece of content can either be a blog post or article. Content must be original and publicly accessible. The blog/article must have at least 2500 characters or more without spaces && 500 words or more. The content must be in English. Content in all languages is accepted  (after the end of Week 5), but non-English submissions are capped at a maximum of 50% (max. reward 1.5 Stakes). Do not submit translated content; do not submit the same content on multiple sites. Doing either of these can result in previous valid entries from being rejected. Maximum of 3 valid entries per participant. The content must contain at least 2 links to the Vena Network website. Low quality content won't receive any stakes. Your submitted ETH address must be in the content description. Both the bounty managers and the Vena team members reserve the right to exclude any submissions.   Rewards The rewards are based on quality (determined by BM) will be paid in the following 3 stages: Standard/completementary: 1-3 Stakes Exceptional: 5-6 Stakes   How to Apply Create the content and then submit it here.  Spreadsheet (Blog and Article)   Vena Video Campaign Rules The video must be original and publicly accessible. The video must be in English. Videos in all languages is accepted  (after the end of Week 5), but non-English submissions are capped at a maximum of 50% (max. reward 3 Stakes). Do not submit translated content; do not submit the same content on multiple sites. Doing either of these can result in previous valid entries from being rejected. The video must be at least 3 minutes long. The video must NOT have a software-generated voice. If the video is animated only (no human voice), it MUST be extremely well animated or it will be removed. Maximum of 2 valid entries per participant. The video must contain at least 2 links to the Vena Network website. Low quality entries won't receive any stakes. Your submitted ETH address must be in the video description. Both the bounty managers and the Vena team members reserve the right to exclude any submissions.   Rewards The rewards are based on quality (determined by BM) will be paid in the following 3 stages: Standard: 0.5-2 Stakes Complementary: 2-3 Stakes Exceptional: 5-6 Stakes   How to Apply Create the video and then submit it here.  Spreadsheet (Video)   Vena Telegram Campaign Rules No spamming of any kind (especially ref. links). Must stay in group until the spreadsheet is finalized. (Optional) Add "Vena.network" to your name. Be active!   Rewards Simple participant (only joins the chat) - 1 stake. Added "Vena.network" to your name - 3 stakes. Active supporter - +5 stakes.   How to Apply Join the Telegram group here and fill in the Google form here.  Telegram sheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1rB-GgZZBVH7_oB3EcEzbqZqdrALaqN11OzBelt_bAnw/edit?usp=sharing   Vena Lucky Draw Campaign How to Apply Visit the Lucky Draw Website and follow the instructions found there.   Vena Translation Campaign Rules One reservation per person. Translations must be original. The ANN thread and Whitepaper must be done within 3 weeks. We reserve the right to reject a reservation, and translation if the quality isn't sufficient.  Rewards 1 stake per entry/language.  How to Apply Submit your application using the linked form here. You will be contacted directly if you are chosen for a given language. Cancelled.  Languages needed To-be-listed. Apply with the language that you usually translate in for now.   Spreadsheet (Translations) Cancelled.   Vena Signature Campaign Rules Minimum of 10 posts must be made weekly. Posts must be at least 100 characters long. Posts must be constructive and not re-state what other people have said. Negative trust accounts are not allowed to participate. If you receive a negative trust during your time in the campaign, you will be removed. The use of alternate accounts is not allowed. Spamming is not tolerated at any cost. Advertising anything else in your signature will get you removed from the campaign. Having 100% of your posts in local boards in any week will most likely result in you receiving 0 stakes for that week.   Rewards Jr. Member - 1 stake weekly Member - 2 stakes weekly Full Member - 4 stakes weekly Senior Member - 7 stakes weekly Hero/Legendary Member - 10 stakes weekly 3 stakes extra weekly if wearing avatar.  How to Apply Wear the signature and fill in the Google form here. Then you can start making posts.
